summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the Board of Park Commissioners of the City of Seattle to acquire by private purchase, in the name of the City of Seattle, a certain portion of the Northeast one-fourth (N. E. 1/4) of Section Twenty-one (21), Township Twenty-five (25) North, Range Four (4) East, W. M., in the City of Seattle, at a price not to exceed Two Thousand Dollars ($2,000.00) cash.
